issue.title: Allow custom frame numbers on the timeline
issue.body:
Currently, you can change the timeline FPS, but the frame number on the timeline does not allow to be customized. So no matter what FPS is set to, at a certain zoom level, the frame number will appear as a multiple of 5, like 5, 10, 15, 20... or a multiple of 10, like 10, 20, 30, 40... However, if the FPS is set to 24, multiples of 4, such as 4, 8, 12, 16..., or multiples of 12, such as 12, 24, 36, 48..., may be more convenient. It would be great to add the setting to customize frame numbers for these cases.

Related post:
http://esotericsoftware.com/forum/Timeline-dopesheet-graph-number-scale-17761

pull_request.title: recolor roadmap course missing prerequisite color
pull_request.body:
## Description
currently, there are inconsistencies with the roadmap and search bar where if a course has incomplete prerequisites, on the search bar the name and units are blue, but the icon is red

on the roadmap, however, the name, icon, and units are all orange

that is, the colors are different, and which elements are colored are also different

changed where the color is applied and the logic for applying color on missing prerequisites, now the units is always displayed as blue, the course name and icon are red

changing the logic had the side effect of fixing another inconsistency where when dragging a course which has incomplete prerequisites, the course name and icon would appear as blue while being dragged. now, the course title and icon will be colored while being dragged as well

## Screenshots
before:
![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2355592b-1724-427c-afb1-24fce0fae651)
![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/5542bada-48ea-4348-8575-ee6a78908bd3)

after:
![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/ce9fed63-c41a-45d9-9af7-67b303d297db)
![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/85d12fa7-f287-49fe-9954-4ffb438012a8)
![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c34197ff-0169-4383-ba56-42e1a176f9b1)


## Test Plan
- [ ] course name + icon red
- [ ] trashcan red only on hover
- [ ] consistent on sidebar + roadmap

## Issues
Closes #640
